'''拟噬人鲨属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|a|''Carcharocles''}}），是一类已[[灭绝|灭绝]]、类似于[[噬人鲨|噬人鲨属]]的[[软骨鱼|软骨鱼]]，属于[[鼠鲨目|鼠鲨目]][[耳齒鯊科|耳齒鯊科]]。

[[巨齿鲨|巨齿鲨]]是[[新近纪|新近纪]]海洋的[[顶尖掠食者|顶尖掠食者]]，本属的其他成员也不遑多让，例如体型也不小的[[丘布特凯克鲨|丘布特拟噬人鲨]]及[[耳基拟噬人鲨|耳基拟噬人鲨]]等<ref>{{cite book |author=Joseph S. Nelson |year=2006 |title=Fishes of the World |edition=4th |publisher=[[John_Wiley_and_Sons|John Wiley and Sons]] |isbn=978-0-471-25031-9 |chapter=Order Lamniformes |pages=57–60 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-bO-2unzU-8C&pg=PA57 |access-date=2018-02-21 |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810195939/https://books.google.com/books?id=-bO-2unzU-8C&pg=PA57 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 分类 ==
目前为止，拟噬人鲨属仅确认六个物种：
*''Carcharocles aksuaticus'' <small>(Menner, 1928)</small>
*''Carcharocles sokolovi'' <small>Ma Jaekel, 1895</small>
*[[丘布特凯克鲨|丘布特拟噬人鲨]] ''Carcharocles chubutensis''<br>{{small|Agassiz 1843}}
*[[安格斯迪鲨|狭齿拟噬人鲨]] ''Carcharocles angustidens''<br>{{small|[[Louis_Agassiz|Agassiz]] 1843}}
*[[耳基拟噬人鲨|耳基拟噬人鲨]] ''Carcharocles auriculatus''<br>{{small|Jordan 1923}}
*[[巨牙鲨|巨齿拟噬人鲨]] ''Carcharocles megalodon''，或简称'''[[巨牙鲨|巨齿鲨]]'''。<br>{{small|Agassiz 1843}}
